The charcoal rojak is very good as the prawn paste is thick n fragrant. Pleasant person making it. May take some time as he is the only one and takes effort in preparing it.

Both charcoal BBQ and rojak available. You can add extra Bbq cuttlefish. Century egg is also nice.
Average coffee shop with good food. Don't like it when we have to self-service for the drinks. I usually don't buy the drink when nobody ask.
Average hokkien mee. The prawn noodles has good soup but not the noodles.
Nice porridge . Highly recommended.  Try it ! I had the pork porridge although the stall also has many others including their signature porridge .
